# Digital Workspace Automation — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

An event-driven file routing system that watches `~/Kiza/desktop/Inbox/`, classifies files using a **Mistral → Grok → OpenRouter** intelligence chain, moves them to categorized folders, and logs to Notion.

