## How to Use

```bash
# Create folders only
python workspace_main.py --setup

# Simulate without moving (safe test)
python workspace_main.py --scan --dry-run

# One-shot scan
python workspace_main.py --scan

# Start real-time watcher (default)
python workspace_main.py
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Before live mode, update [.env](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/.env) with real `GROK_API_KEY`, `NOTION_API_KEY`, and `NOTION_DATABASE_ID`.
